OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FChance of a light shower at
OL,6,Ffirst. Otherwise it will be a dry day
OL,7,Fwith variable amounts of cloud and
OL,8,Fsunny spells. Warm in the sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,11,Fsome late sunshine in places. Then the
OL,12,Frest of the night will be dry and
OL,13,Frather cloudy. Freshening westerly
OL,14,Fbreeze later.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FMainly dry and cloudy, chance
OL,17,Fof a light shower at first. Becoming
OL,18,Fsomewhat brighter in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
