OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Saturday with some patchy light
OL,7,Frain, this mainly across the west.
OL,8,FMainly dry, bright and breezy on
OL,9,FSunday. Chance of some rain on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
